CHENODIA.

SPRATTUS ET UXOR.

JAcK SPRATT could eat no sat, His wife could eat no lean, And so between them both They licked the platter clean.

Sprattus horrescens adipem recusat,

Uxor et non vult tolerare macrum:

Conjuges digni! potuere sic de- tergere lancem.
